description:
Have you ever wanted to cram for a college exam in 24 hours?

If you have, would you like to replicate this tense experience?

Now you can, for some reason, in SUPER STUDY CRAM SESH! (a totally accurate college exam study simulator).

The full title is necessary to say, yes.

I made  this for an assignment for my CDM 072 class. Feel free to let me know what you think :)
